'''Praya''' (frah di [[Latn|Latn]] ''precari'' "fi ax oernisli, beg, inchriit")<ref>Harper, Douglas [http://www.etymonline.com/index.php?/ pray], Online Etymology Dictionary, axes 30 December 2014</ref> a invuokieshan ar ak we siik fi achiiv rapuor wid wah abjek a [[Woship|woship]] chuu dilibaret komiunikieshan.

Praya kiah bi a faam a [[Rilijan|rilijos praktis]], ah kiah bi aida indivijal ar kamiunal ah tek plies ina poblik ar ina praivit. Ikiah invalv di yuus a wod, sing ar kompliit sailans. Wen [[Languij|languij]] yuuz, praya kiah tek di faam a im, inkiantieshan, faamal kriidal stietment, ar spantienios otarans frah di smadi uu a-prie. A difrah-difrah faam a praya laka pitishan praya, praya a soplikieshan, tangxgivin, ah priez. Praya kiah dairek tuwadz wah [[Diyiti|diyiti]], pirit, disiis smadi, ar lafti aidie, fi di poerpos a woship, rikues gaidans, rikues asistans, kanfes chranzgreshan ([[Sin|sin]]) ar fi smadi expres deh taat ah imuoshan. So dwiin, piipl prie fi wuoliip a riizn laka poersnal benifit, fi ax fi  divain gries, [[Pirichualiti|pirichual kanekshan]], ar fi di siek a smadi els.

